Package org.tensorics.core.tree.domain

Class RebuildingContextImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tensorics.core.tree.domain.RebuildingContextImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RebuildingContext
    public class RebuildingContextImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements RebuildingContext
    RebuildingContextImpl implements RebuildingContext storing the relation from an old node to the new node in a Map in which the key is the old node.
